## Limitations

The information gathered is based on available online resources, which may not encompass all perspectives or the latest research on the topic. Additionally, the sources used are primarily educational websites and essays, which may lack the depth and rigor of peer-reviewed academic studies. Further research, including interviews with survivors and analysis of scholarly articles, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the long-term effects of the Holocaust.